snippet.title: Birdlingo: a birdsong learning game - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://birdlingo.com
Immerse yourself in a cute and relaxing atmosphere as you learn the songs of the 44 most common birds in Europe.
Birdlingo is free and available in French and English.
